{"tid":1666667,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 可無限上傳原相片   Google Photos 確認是 Bug 作怪","createTime":"2019-10-21T05:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T10:25:30.000Z","uid":167573,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"79c9a8984d570cf4f7632dde4bc2a1dce3fc6c89","tid":1666667,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"昨日我們報導過 Google Photos 被投訴，自家 Pixel 4 手機並不支援無限上載原尺寸相片，但 iPhone 用戶則可以獲得無限上載的優待。外國傳媒報導後引起了不少迴響，Google 向網站 Android Police 發聲明，表示一切都是 Bug 作怪，並且會在稍後修復漏洞。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 在聲明中表示 iOS 版本的 Google Photos 程式再上載原尺寸相片時，並沒有正確計算用戶的 Google Drive 儲存空間用量，令用戶在用完他們的 15GB 免費空間後，毋須因此額外繳費。由於 Apple 用作儲存相片的 HEIC 檔案格式，較 Google 的「高質量」JPEG 格式更慳位，所以 Google 直接將 HEIC 檔案上傳，不過在實際轉儲存時，卻佔用更多空間和耗費更長轉換時間。Google 表明將會修復這漏洞，但就未有透露會如何執行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/10/21/google-to-fix-bug-that-lets-iphones-store-full-quality-photos/software/ios-app/?fbclid=IwAR16msFCtvyt33dSjVyv10W6Hi-PAkiXAMNujXFyWWNskxu5SlhRxafG6NU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F21%2Fgoogle-to-fix-bug-that-lets-iphones-store-full-quality-photos%2Fsoftware%2Fios-app%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR16msFCtvyt33dSjVyv10W6Hi-PAkiXAMNujXFyWWNskxu5SlhRxafG6NU&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERdAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=15afd3d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/10/21/google-to-fix-bug-that-lets-iphones-store-full-quality-photos/software/ios-app/?fbclid=IwAR16msFCtvyt33dSjVyv10W6Hi-PAkiXAMNujXFyWWNskxu5SlhRxafG6NU</a>"},{"pid":"cf7a3115c7c7784a5c6def0531253b4c91f8308c","tid":1666667,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:39:48.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8436a78440edccbb10c2eefe5c75e7a0b06d09","tid":1666667,"uid":22822,"